<Layout title="About AmicBridge">
  <section style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1rem; text-align: left;">
    <h1 style="font-size: 2.4rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #1b263b;">
      About AmicBridge
    </h1>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      <strong>AmicBridge</strong> is a research and intelligence company focused on helping investors make smarter, faster, and more confident financial decisions.
      We specialize in providing verified data and analysis about the <strong>crypto market</strong> and other emerging asset classes.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      By subscribing to our insights, you gain access to carefully researched information — not hype.
      We break down complex market data into clear investment signals and show you
      which opportunities have the strongest potential to grow your capital.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      Every analysis we publish includes a <strong>probability rating</strong> — a percentage that reflects how likely an asset or project is to deliver
      profitable returns based on market conditions, volume data, innovation strength, and trend momentum.
      This gives our members a measurable way to assess risk before investing.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      At AmicBridge, we don’t take your investments or hold your funds.
      Instead, for a small fee, we give you access to high-quality intelligence that guides you toward smarter, safer, and potentially more profitable decisions.
      The information you receive is designed to help you see what others miss — so you can act early, confidently, and strategically.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
      Whether you’re focused on <strong>crypto, commodities, real estate, or emerging technologies</strong>,
      AmicBridge helps you understand where money is moving, why it’s moving there, and how you can position yourself ahead of the curve.
    </p>

    <p style="text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: #0056b3; margin-top: 2rem;">
      AmicBridge — Turning Market Knowledge into Financial Growth.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
